pt_warehouse - is the first experimental PropTricks map of mine. 
Was done in about 6 hours while watching series.
Tier: 1
Length: Short

What is PropTricks gamemode?

PropTricks is a competitive gamemode (includes timer) where the main goal is to push different props (mostly crates) to the endzone. 
You are able to choose whatever route you think suits you.

The gamemode currently is in Closed Alpha.
